# cowsay

Cowsay in Python

## Installation

```sh
pip install wagjo-cowsay
```

## Usage

Available announcers: cow, tux, cat, owl, horse, dog, elephant, monkey

```sh
cowsay
cowsay "Hello World"
cowsay -t -a dog
cowsay -c red -a cat "Hi there!"
echo "I hopy you have a nice day sir" | cowsay -
```

